content:
Dear Sheffield City Council,
Please provide the following relating to the City Centre Development known as the 'Heart of the City'
At 31 August, 2024:-
The numbers of let and vacant street level units;
The numbers of vacant and let non-street level, non-residential units;
The total floor areas of the let and vacant units referred to above;
The terms of any rental incentives (without any names of tenants) offered to potential and current occupiers of street level units;
The numbers of let and vacant residential units constructed as part of this scheme.
At end of the last complete financial year:
The total expenditure from all sources to complete the HoS2 scheme;
The total debt incurred by SCC to enable the scheme's completion;
The term and interest rate of any debt specifically associated with HoS2 whether secured on it or not.
Yours faithfully,
Albert Thwiepp
